en_313186_0	10 Sri Lanka Light Infantry (SLLI) troops of the 653 Brigade under the Security Force Headquarters – Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) extended their assistance on Monday (11) to clean the Ambalpuram Tamil School premises at Anandapuram in Kilinochchi.
en_313186_1	The ‘Shramadana’ programme was organized under the supervision of Major General Kumara Peiris, General Officer Commanding, 65 Division and Colonel Robin Jayasooriya, Brigade Commander, 653 Brigade.
en_313186_2	Around 30 troops of 10 SLLI voluntarily took part in the ‘Shramadana’ campaign at the request of authorities.
